* No phone-home tracking; no license gates in free plugin.
* Pro upsell: link only (readme + settings), no crippleware.
* `readme.txt`: Contributors **brelandr**, NIV copyright block, FAQ, changelog.
* Assets: `assets/icon-256x256.png`, `icon-128x128.png`, banners per `assets/README.md`.
* PHPUnit: `tests/THW_Curriculum_Test.php` must pass before zip (`create-plugin-zip.sh`).
* Exclude from zip: `.cursorrules`, `.git/`, `tests/`, `vendor/` (dev), `composer.json`, `*.md`, `*.sh`.

